    <item>
      <title>叙利亚战火重燃，谁在战斗？为何战斗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/syrian-civil-war-who-s-fighting-and-why-in-the-revived-conflict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚内战于 2011 年爆发，经过四年的平静之后，战火再次燃起。叛军从总统巴沙尔·阿萨德的政权手中夺取了阿勒颇市，另一个叛军组织从叙利亚库尔德人手中夺取了该市北部一座较小的城市，打破了该国各敌对派系之间紧张的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/syrian-civil-war-who-s-fighting-and-why-in-the-revived-conflict</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 22:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼宣布向乌克兰提供价值 7.25 亿美元的新武器计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-to-announce-725-million-arms-package-for-ukraine-including-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼周一宣布了从美国库存中抽取的最新一批向乌克兰提供的武器，总额为 7.25 亿美元，其中包括总统乔·拜登批准的第二批杀伤人员地雷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/us-to-announce-725-million-arms-package-for-ukraine-including-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 16:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国最高外交官称中国制造的无人机损害欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/german-foreign-minister-says-chinese-made-drones-hurting-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国最高外交官表示，俄罗斯在乌克兰使用的中国制造的无人机正在伤害欧洲，在欧盟可能公布制裁措施之前，她对这个亚洲国家的批评进一步加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/german-foreign-minister-says-chinese-made-drones-hurting-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 09:37:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
